---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---
<PageLayout
  title="Still Unsure? — Syvidea"
  description="Three ways to get unstuck and find the right workstation configuration."
>
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-20 pb-24 sm:pt-28 sm:pb-32">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-dark-999"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 cyber-bg"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-bg opacity-20"></div>
    <div class="glow-bg top-10 left-1/3 h-96 w-96 bg-neon-purple/20 animate-glow-pulse"></div>

    <div class="container-page relative">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
        <div class="mb-5 flex justify-center">
          <span class="badge">Decision support</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-balance text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
          <span class="gradient-text">Still not sure</span>
          <br />
          <span class="text-white">which configuration fits?</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-400 text-balance">
          Let us help you get back on track. Choose the path that feels most comfortable.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Section
    eyebrow="Get back on track"
    title="Three ways to find your answer"
    align="left"
  >
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <a href="/use-cases" onclick="trackEvent('abandoned_intent', { action: 'revisit_use_cases' })" class="group card border-neon-purple/30 bg-dark-900/50 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all">
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-neon-purple/20 text-neon-purple">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 6v6m0 0v6m0-6h6m-6 0H6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Go back to Use Cases</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
            Map your workload to hardware by exploring real use cases.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-neon-purple">
            Explore use cases
            <svg class="ml-1 h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12" />
              <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/recommendation-engine" onclick="trackEvent('abandoned_intent', { action: 'try_recommendation' })" class="group card border-neon-cyan/30 bg-dark-900/50 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all">
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-neon-cyan/20 text-neon-cyan">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2" ry="2" />
              <line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="9" />
              <line x1="9" y1="15" x2="15" y2="15" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Try simplified recommendation</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
            Answer 2-3 quick questions for a tailored hardware recommendation.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-neon-cyan">
            Get recommendation
            <svg class="ml-1 h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12" />
              <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/request-quote" onclick="trackEvent('abandoned_intent', { action: 'request_manual_help' })" class="group card border-neon-orange/30 bg-dark-900/50 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all">
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-neon-orange/20 text-neon-orange">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Talk to us (manual review)</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
            Get human guidance to find the right configuration for your specific needs.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-neon-orange">
            Request manual review
            <svg class="ml-1 h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12" />
              <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section
    eyebrow="Quick reminder"
    title="What all three options share"
    align="left"
  >
    <div class="card">
      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="p-4">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-neon-purple">Same architecture</div>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">All run AMD Strix Halo / AI Max+ 395</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-neon-cyan">Same capabilities</div>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Local LLM, RAG, agents, multimodal</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-neon-orange">Same process</div>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Quote-based with human validation</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-20">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-dark-999"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 cyber-bg"></div>

    <div class="container-page relative">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
          <span class="gradient-text">Ready to take the next step?</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg text-slate-400">
          We are here to help you find the right configuration for your AI workload.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/recommendation-engine" onclick="trackEvent('abandoned_intent', { action: 'cta_recommendation' })" class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center justify-center">
            Start recommendation
            <svg class="ml-2 h-4 w-4" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12" />
              <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/request-quote" onclick="trackEvent('abandoned_intent', { action: 'cta_request_quote' })" class="btn-secondary inline-flex items-center justify-center">
            Request quote directly
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>